    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in solid, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts exactly as it should, making for a dependable daily driver. While the exterior paint shows some minor stone chips and the interior has light wear consistent with regular use, there are no major mechanical issues or accidents to report. It features a clean title, a complete service history, and a set of tires with plenty of tread remaining. Buyers can expect a high-quality, honest car that is ready for many more miles on the road.",
