    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional vehicle preserved in showroom condition. This specimen exhibits uncompromising aesthetic and mechanical integrity, having been curated to the most exacting standards of automotive excellence. With an immaculate interior and a flawless exterior finish, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the collector who demands absolute perfection. Experience the pinnacle of its class in a state that remains indistinguishable from new.",
